sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant MLPod as ML Workload Pod
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over MLPod, S3: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking

    MLPod->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>Proxy: Validate SA Token
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>HTTP/5000 (pod-local, plaintext)
    MLflow->>MLflow: Resolve workspace from<br/>X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE header
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow-->>Proxy: 200 OK (Run metadata)
    Proxy-->>MLPod: 200 OK

    MLPod->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-batch<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>HTTP/5000
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT metrics, params, tags<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, TLS 1.2+
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact files<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM / Access Key
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Proxy: 200 OK
    Proxy-->>MLPod: 200 OK

    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FedUI as MLflow Federated UI
    participant MFAPI as MLflow API<br/>via Platform Gateway

    Note over Browser, MFAPI: Flow 2: UI Embedding via Module Federation

    Browser->>Dashboard: Navigate to Experiments<br/>HTTPS/443, OAuth/OIDC
    Dashboard->>FedUI: Load remoteEntry.js<br/>HTTPS via Gateway, Bearer Token
    FedUI-->>Dashboard: MlflowExperimentWrapper
    Dashboard->>MFAPI: GET /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    MFAPI-->>Dashboard: Experiment list (JSON)

    participant OTELApp as OTEL-instrumented App
    participant MLflowOTLP as MLflow /v1/traces<br/>5000/TCP HTTP

    Note over OTELApp, PG: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    OTELApp->>MLflowOTLP: POST /v1/traces<br/>HTTP/5000, Bearer Token<br/>Content-Type: application/x-protobuf
    MLflowOTLP->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, TLS 1.2+
    PG-->>MLflowOTLP: OK
    MLflowOTLP-->>OTELApp: 200 OK

    participant Client as Client Application
    participant GW as MLflow AI Gateway<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, LLM: Flow 4: AI Gateway LLM Proxy

    Client->>GW: POST /gateway/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/5000, Bearer Token
    GW->>GW: Decrypt provider API key<br/>(KEK envelope encryption)
    GW->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, Provider API Key
    LLM-->>GW: Streaming SSE response
    GW-->>Client: Proxied SSE response
